metadata.name: Lost Souls
metadata.description:
Who am I within this collective?
Is an unlit light still a light bulb?
Is a broken rock still a rock?
How to name what distorts traditional programming?
Hack our drives, genetically programmed, compulsive, inherited.
The break is a time frame.
It occurs when matter does not fit in a body that wanders towards yours route.
In firm steps there is also imbalance. It takes courage, whatever the landscape.
In this game of concepts, the compositions embrace each other outlining the colored geometry. The figures that live in the head for a long time; months, sometimes years, tell things that were not yet in the superficial layer of the rational.

3000x2000

The first owner will receive a framed poster sized artwork and a NFT avatar inspired by this scene to be released on Opensea in 2022. Additionally, access to whitelist of planned exclusive fashion items inspired by my NFT works.
